title: Looking for Bronze/Silver team
body:
Hey I'm a Silver 5 looking to try out ranked teams. I'm on most nights from 9.30 til late qld time, and as long as I'm not working I'm available earlier. I mainly just want to have some fun games where everyone is on the same page.

Top: Irelia, Gnar, Trundle
Mid: Orianna, Galio
Support: Lulu, Alistair, Nami, Leona

 Add me in game at Juicydangler
